<br />
Ok I got it.  It just needed to be this 
<br />
require_once 'bbantispam.php'; 
<br />
with no folder.  The files needed to be in the forum folder directory.
<br />

<br />
Now captcha isn't showing up?  Any clues?  Could anything else go wrong?
<br />

<br />
Nevermind!  I just reset the config and renabled the visual confirmation and now captcha magically works again.  Go figure!
<br />

<br />
This MOD was easy, yet difficult!
<br />

<br />
Thanks to all who attempted to help me.  The whole problem was having the extra folder named bbantispam.
<br />

<br />
